description: Watch out everyone! The bad guys are here! In the second exciting issue of the official Star Wars Rebels magazine, we'll have the complete lowdown on the Empire's scariest villains from Agent Kallus to the deadly Inquisitor. Oh, and not forgetting Darth Vader! Look out for plenty of fun and games as well, along with an amazing comic strip you won't want to miss!

Are you ready for another Star Wars Rebels adventure? Zoom inside the awesome issue and test your skills in our brain-busting puzzles! Pitch Rebels against Imperials in our amazing game. Discover what happens to young Ezra when he strays too far from home, and a couple of bounty hunters try their luck in the action packed comic strip. All this plus character profiles, data files, and an incredible giveaway! Available in Newsstand and PREVIEWS Exclusive editions.
